         "text": [
            {
               "text": "### Images from ANTT\n\nThese images are copyright for ANTT and allowed to be used according to the license determined by them.\n\nTo visualize all images, use the left and right arrows on the slide below.",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "markdown",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p><div class=\"htSlides\"><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">1 / 5</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"ArmsMaertin\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('ArmsMaertin', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Arms of Maertim Lem (<htcite0>). <span id=\"ANTTPortugal2\"></span></div><div class=\"htSlideRefs\"><b>Related content:</b><ul><li>Lem/Leme - We explore the family’s history, including their involvement in the Treaty of Tordesillas and the Paulista Civil War. (<htcite7>)</li></ul></div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">2 / 5</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"ArmsAntonio\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('ArmsAntonio', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Arms of Antonio Leme (<htcite1>). <span id=\"ANTTPortugal1\"></span></div><div class=\"htSlideRefs\"><b>Related content:</b><ul><li>Lem/Leme - We explore the family’s history, including their involvement in the Treaty of Tordesillas and the Paulista Civil War. (<htcite7>)</li></ul></div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">3 / 5</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"PDPFamilyTree\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('PDPFamilyTree', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Genealogical tree attached to the diligence of Pedro Dias Paes (<htcite2>). <span id=\"ANTTPortugal3\"></span></div><div class=\"htSlideRefs\"><b>Related content:</b><ul><li>Lem/Leme - We explore the family’s history, including their involvement in the Treaty of Tordesillas and the Paulista Civil War. (<htcite7>)</li><li>The image will be used in a new game, which is still in development.</li></ul></div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">4 / 5</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgANTTINCOMPLETE\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgANTTINCOMPLETE', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Incomplete habilitation for the Order of Christ (<htcite3>). © Arquivo Nacional Torre do Tombo (<htcite4>).</div><div class=\"htSlideRefs\"><b>Related content:</b><ul><li>The image will be used in a new game, which is still in development.</li></ul></div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">5 / 5</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"RP\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('RP', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Bula present in the Arquivo Nacional da Torre do Tombo, Lisboa, Portugal (<htcite5>).</div><div class=\"htSlideRefs\"><b>Related content:</b><ul><li>Slavery overview - Unfortunately, slavery was part of human history for millennia, and its effects are still felt today. (<htcite6>)</li></ul></div></div><i class=\"fa-solid fa-chevron-left htSlidePrev\" onclick=\"htPlusDivs(-1);\"></i><i class=\"fa-solid fa-chevron-right htSlideNext\" onclick=\"htPlusDivs(1);\"></i></div></p>",
